<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1436,1735,2026]" lastBlockId="13.[247,831,158,184]" lastPageId="13" lastPageNumber="14" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">
<emphasis box="[247,344,2000,2025]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Habitat.</emphasis>
Agricultural areas invaded by grasses (
<bibRefCitation author="Lindberg" box="[825,1015,2000,2026]" pageId="12" pageNumber="27" refString="Lindberg, H. (1961) Hemiptera Insularum Madeirensium. Commentationes Biologicae, 24 (1), 1 - 82." type="journal article" year="1961">
