<number box="[952,1015,2000,2026]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" value="1961.0">1961</number>
</bibRefCitation>
). A vector of phytoplasmas and/or spiroplasmas (
<bibRefCitation author="Boukhris-Bouhachem" box="[415,819,158,184]" pageId="13" pageNumber="26" refString="Boukhris-Bouhachem, S., Chabbouh, N., Mounira, Harbi &amp; Jean-Luc, Danet (2007). The leafhoppers potential vectors of phytopathogene agents in Tunesian vineyards (Hemiptera: Cicadomorpha: Fulguromorpha). Annales de la Societe Entomologique de France, 43 (2), 159 - 163." type="journal article" year="2007">
Boukhris-Bouhachem 
<emphasis box="[681,733,159,184]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">et al</emphasis>
